description: A person visiting on compassionate grounds tested positive while self-isolating, the government says.
title: Coronavirus: Visitor to Isle of Man tests positive for Covid-19
title_page: Coronavirus: Visitor to Isle of Man tests positive for Covid-19 - BBC News
maintext: Five people have tested positive since the first case in more than 100 days was recorded on 6 September and the number of active cases on the island currently stands at two.
